subject: United States Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal, seeking to complete the career Grand Slam, will be the top-seeded man when the U.S. Open starts, while Roger Federer will be seeded second, followed by Novak Djokovic and Andy Murray.
